{"tid":979731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港街馬23歲跑手比賽期間暈倒　送院急救","createTime":"2019-01-13T02:55:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T03:00:51.000Z","uid":41404,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"82262500eb5fc5946fe7d9c0047fc701e68aa18f","tid":979731,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:55:41.000Z","msg":"「香港街馬2019」於今晨舉行期間，一名23歲男跑手，在啟德隧道附近比賽期間突然暈倒，並陷入昏迷，在場的聖約翰救傷隊人員立即為跑手急救，並送往伊利沙伯醫院搶救。「香港街馬2019」賽事包括8公里及半馬拉松，以觀塘繞道作起點，觀塘海濱道公園及土瓜灣遊樂場為終點。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/bkn-20190113095623726-0113_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190113%2Fbkn-20190113095623726-0113_00822_001.html&d=0H4oW%2BgquIP99nIvOe5VJS7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=339ada59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190113/bkn-20190113095623726-0113_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"fb1f360a946cdc61e5f9a93e5bec84f1940cc2ea","tid":979731,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"god bless"},{"pid":"afc9efd084bee83dfce548cd713af477daab68a1","tid":979731,"uid":40470,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T02:57:26.000Z","msg":"本身仲諗仲一路跑一路打咭呃like溝女<br />\n<br />\n今次柒左點收科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3dafe20ee9ac15e4752d178141675b548cee931","tid":979731,"uid":20867,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:03:36.000Z","msg":"毒霧襲港仲敢街跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://p1.pstatp.com/large/400d0004612bfabc1b77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fp1.pstatp.com%2Flarge%2F400d0004612bfabc1b77&h=46290881&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b9a9c5f7643f2d6d90a1c1813144cdd4621a691","tid":979731,"uid":205462,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-13T03:05:43.000Z","msg":"呢排空氣質素咁